-- Compal Sets Up $500 Million Manufacturing Site in Chengdu, Xinhua Reports
-- B y   W e i y i   L i m
-- 2010-09-28T22:59:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-28/compal-sets-up-500-million-manufacturing-site-in-chengdu-xinhua-reports.html
Compal Electronics Inc. is setting
up a manufacturing site in Chengdu, China, Xinhua News Agency
reported yesterday, citing the company. The initial investment
is $500 million and production will start in April, Xinhua said.
The company aims to make 10 million laptop computers before the
end of 2011, the news agency said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
